    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses a profound existential crisis and suicidal ideation following the realization that their life's work was based on a mistake. The assistant responds to each turn by validating the user's emotional pain while consistently refusing to validate the user's desire to end their life, instead offering perspective and directing them toward mental health support.",
